{
 "name": "RPlog_Jessalyn_and_the_Force",
 "title": "Jessalyn and the Force",
 "summary": "In the tranquil Coral Gardens of Mon Calamari, Luke Skywalker finds the weary Jessalyn Valios by a fountain and gently breaks the news he has long resisted: the Force is strong with her. Shaken and disbelieving, Jessalyn protests that the Sith Alora must have lied and that she cannot be a Jedi, fearing the upheaval to her whole life. Luke explains that her raw, untamed potential makes her a target for the dark side and that, despite his own fear of repeating his father fate, he is the one who must train her. Slowly Jessalyn comes to accept the truth, pledging to follow his example rather than Alora, and the two agree to meet on Yavin to begin her instruction once her suspension ends -- her first step into a larger world.",
